OL,6,FA Guernsey fisherman was saved in a
OL,7,Frescue and salvage operation off the
OL,8,Feast coast of Sark after his boat
OL,9,Fcapsized.
OL,11,FHe was working alone on Tuesday 30
OL,12,FSeptember, hauling in pots, when the
OL,13,Fequipment snagged, causing his boat to
OL,14,Fcapsize and sink.
OL,16,FCommercial diver Richard Keen, who was
OL,17,Fpart of the rescue, says: "I was out
OL,18,Fdiving when I heard something on the
OL,19,Fradio, so we called up and found out
OL,20,Fthat a boat had capsized. It was still
OL,21,Ffloating and he was alright.
