OL,6,F"I made a phone call, three men showed
OL,7,Fup, and we shot across."
OL,9,FAt midday on Tuesday, Guernsey
OL,10,FCoastguard says it received a phone
OL,11,Fcall from a vessel on the west coast
OL,12,Fof Sark, reporting that a 5.5m fishing
OL,13,Fboat had sunk and a person had been
OL,14,Frecovered from the water.
OL,16,FThe fisherman suffered no significant
OL,17,Finjuries and was taken back to St
OL,18,FPeter Port by the inshore lifeboat.
