OL,6,FThe vessel was partly refloated by
OL,7,Fcommercial divers and towed back to
OL,8,FGuernsey, where it has since been
OL,9,Flifted out of the water by a crane.
OL,11,FRichard recalls the rescue,
OL,12,Fexplaining: "It didn't take much to
OL,13,Flift the boat, and I had experience
OL,14,Fwith the same boat because it sank
OL,15,Fabout 10 years ago on the west coast
OL,16,Finto a rock."
OL,18,FHe continues: "We had lots of help,
OL,19,Fpeople wanted to come and help tow it,
OL,20,Fit's a crowd of fishermen here. It's a
OL,21,Fcommunity of people.
