OL,6,F"He was getting his pots back, and the
OL,7,Fnext thing he knew, he was in the
OL,8,Fwater.
OL,10,F"But he's safe, the boat's back, but
OL,11,Fit's a bit of a sad affair. I just
OL,12,Ffeel very sorry for him, he's got a
OL,13,Fyoung family, a seven-week-old baby,
OL,14,Fand you get fished out of the water."
OL,16,FThe Chief Inspector of Marine
OL,17,FAccidents has ordered a safety
OL,18,Finvestigation to identify what caused
OL,19,Fthe incident and to try to prevent
OL,20,Ffuture problems.
